===Deprecated parameters===
The <tt>miniv=1</tt>, <tt>viewplain=1</tt>, <tt>nodiv=1</tt> and <tt>fontcolor=</tt> parameters have been deprecated. To implement the view-only version, use the {{en/tlx|v}} or {{en/tlx|view}} templates instead.

== Notes ==
Navbar is contained within a {{en/tag|div}} in order to accommodate a horizontal unnumbered list. This means it cannot be placed inside a {{en/tag|span}} or other inline element, because Tidy will 'fix' situations where it finds block elements inside inline elements.

== Prepackaged ==
;{{en/tl|Navbar-header}}: Positions {{en/navbar|navbar/doc|mini=1}} on the right edge of the line, often used in non-collapsible navbox heading.
;{{en/tl|Tnavbar-navframe}}: For use in conjunction with [https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/NavFrame Navframe div]s, positions {{en/navbar|navbar/doc|mini=1}} opposite of the [hide]/[show] feature.
;{{en/tl|Navbar-collapsible}}: For use in conjunction with [https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/ NavFrame Collapsible tables], floats {{en/navbar|navbar/doc|mini=1}} opposite of the [hide]/[show] feature.

